---
// Full-width video interlude with Visioneering quote overlay.
---

<section class="relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <div class="relative min-h-[500px] w-full">
    <video
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
      poster="/images/interlude-poster.jpg"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <source src="/videos/interlude.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>

    <!-- Strong dark overlay for text readability -->
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.82)_0%,rgba(0,0,0,0.78)_50%,rgba(0,0,0,0.9)_100%)]"
    ></div>
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"
    ></div>

    <!-- Subtle gold glow -->
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,rgba(212,175,75,0.12)_0%,transparent_70%)]"
    ></div>

    <!-- Gold rail lines top & bottom -->
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-[rgba(212,175,75,0.45)] to-transparent"></div>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-[rgba(212,175,75,0.45)] to-transparent"></div>

    <!-- Visioneering quote overlay -->
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex min-h-[500px] w-full max-w-[1600px] items-center px-6 py-24 md:px-10">
      <div class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-3 reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-bone-muted md:justify-start">
            <span class="text-bone">Visioneering.</span>
            <span class="text-gold-400">(*)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <blockquote
          class="md:col-span-9 md:pl-8 md:border-l md:border-[rgba(212,175,55,0.22)] reveal reveal-delay-1 text-center md:text-left"
        >
          <p
            class="font-display text-[clamp(1.8rem,3.6vw,3rem)] italic font-light leading-[1.2] text-bone"
            style="text-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);"
          >
            <span class="text-gold-gradient">“Vision”</span> meets Walt Disney's <span class="text-gold-gradient">“Imagineering.”</span> It's the magic that happens during brainstorming — where bold ideas, strategy, relationships and resources collide, and the impossible finally feels like…
            <span class="text-shine">an achievable dream.</span>
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-8 text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-bone-muted">
            — The Sabean Group Philosophy
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
